Fashions by Carole Kinoti recently launched the Nairobi Fashion Week. Her designs were showcased at the Norfolk Hotel. Fashion Week presented a range of designs, including luxurious and formal, as well as casual and sporty. Designs include modern kitenge dresses, kaftans, armhole waistcoats and shirt dresses. Kinoti said she was pleased to be part of Norfolk Arts and Cocktail series. â€œWe create authentic and creative outfits that express feelings about an individual, giving a natural feel and easy flow," she said.